TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
What do you know about the plague?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병에 대해 무엇을 아십니까?

TextEng: Have you heard anything about strange creatures in the area?
Text: 이 근처에서 이상한 생명체들에 대해 들은 게 있나요?

TextEng: Do you know anything of interest about Blacklake?
Text: 검은호수 지구에 대해 흥미로운 정보가 있습니까?

TextEng: What you know 'bout plague?
You hears of strange creatures maybe?
You know things 'bout Blacklake?
I'm investigating the plague. Maybe you could help me?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병을 조사 중입니다. 도와주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Maybe you've heard some rumors here in Blacklake about the plague? Odd things, perhaps?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 여기 검은호수에서 역병 관련 소문을 들은 적이 있나요? 이상한 일이라든가요?

TextEng: Me look into plague. Maybe you help?
What kind of odd things do you hear?
I'd be interested in work, if you know of anything.
Are there any places of interest in Blacklake I should visit?
Text: 검은호수에서 찾아가 볼 만한 곳이 있습니까?

TextEng: Odd stuff? What odd stuff you speak of?
Text: 이상한 거? 무슨 이상한 거 말해?

TextEng: Me want work.
You know good places to go here?
Text: 여기 가볼 만한 좋은 곳 알아?

TextEng: Anything you can tell me about the zoo?
Text: 동물원에 대해 알려줄 만한 게 있나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> What about creatures other than at the zoo? Maybe you've heard of something recent?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 동물원 말고 다른 생명체들은요? 최근에 들은 게 있나요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout zoo, then?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, telling me won't do any harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 내게 말해도 해가 될 건 없어요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. Will hurt nobody.
Maybe you could tell me about some recent events.
Text: 최근 일어난 일들에 대해 들려주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me have questions about stuff going on.
Text: 지금 일어나는 거에 대해 질문 있어.

TextEng: I want to ask you something else.
Me have other question.
I need some directions.
Blacklake big place. Me need directions.
Text: 검은호수 큰 곳. 나 길 안내 필요해.

TextEng: Where is the nearest inn?
Where is the nearest temple?
Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Text: 근처에 장비를 살 만한 곳이 있습니까?

TextEng: Me look for place to sleep.
Me look for temple.
Me need place to buy stuff.
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
No, me have other question.
Who are you?
Who you?
So... what, exactly, do you clean?
I thought only nobles lived in Blacklake.
What you clean?
So you've been in every house in the area?
Text: 그럼 이 근처 집들은 다 들어가 보셨다는 건가요?

TextEng: So you go in all these houses?
Text: 그럼 여기 집들 다 들어가 봤어?

TextEng: Are there certain estates you don't go into?
Any noble houses you not like going to?
Text: 안 가고 싶은 귀족 집 있어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Oh, go on. What were you about to say?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 에이, 계속 하시죠. 방금 하려던 말이 뭐였죠?

TextEng: Tell me about the wizard, woman, before you try cleaning without hands.
Text: 마법사에 대해 얘기해, 아줌마. 아니면 손 없이 청소하는 법부터 배우게 될 거야.

TextEng: Could I ask you some other questions?
Text: 다른 질문을 몇 가지 더 드려도 될까요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> No, you say. You can tells me.
You speak 'bout wizard or you cleans without hands!
Text: 마법사 얘기해! 아니면 손 없이 청소해!

TextEng: Me have other questions.
You might know some secrets about Meldanen, then?
Text: 그럼 멜다넨에 관한 비밀도 좀 알고 계신가요?

TextEng: If he snuck you into the estate, perhaps that entrance still exists?
Text: 그가 당신을 저택으로 몰래 들여보냈다면, 그 출입구가 아직 남아 있을까요?

TextEng: You knows wizard's secrets?
I am grateful. Take these ten gold pieces as a gift from me.
Text: 고맙습니다. 제 선물로 금화 10개를 받아 주십시오.

TextEng: Me thought only nobles in Blacklake.
Text: 나 검은호수엔 귀족만 있는 줄 알았어.

TextEng: If he snuck yous in, maybe backdoor thingy still work?
Text: 그가 너 몰래 들여보냈으면, 어쩌면 뒷문 통로 아직 통할 거 아니야?

TextEng: Me thank yous. Here, you gets ten golds.
